{
    "comment_thread": {}, 
    "video_length": "PT10M58S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "[ Music ]", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ Applause ]", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&gt;&gt; Seung Chan Lim: For the first, for the last past 5 years", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of my life, I&#39;ve been spending time, both inside and outside", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of graduate school, conducting research on what it means", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make something, how it works as a creative process,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and why it matters to our lives.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to do the research,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I left the field of information technology", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to attend an art school, to study both visual", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and performing arts.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what I&#39;d like to do today is share two of the stories", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from that experience and relate it back", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the idea of going further.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So on the second day of grad school,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was sitting in a classroom surrounded", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by freshman students.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was kind of nervous at the time,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because at the time I was 31 and they were 18.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my art skills were crappy.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had no background in art", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I couldn&#39;t draw to save my life.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But thankfully, for the first assignment,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the instructor started off by showing us a simple demo", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of how to properly fold a piece of paper.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was like, I totally got this.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But then after the demo she turned to us and said, &quot;Okay,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "now go fold something&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was like, go fold what?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And she said, &quot;Whatever you want&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I froze.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, for almost a decade before coming", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to graduate school, I had clients giving me problems", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to solve.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;ve never quite gotten a problem", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like fold whatever you want.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what was I supposed to do?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I went back to my desk and started to brainstorm.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I sketched as many different designs as I possibly could,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hoping I could get to something that was good.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I couldn&#39;t.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Six hours passed by and I just sat there,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with all my energy drained,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "unable to figure out what I should fold.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But then I noticed something.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I saw a girl sitting at the far away corner of the studio,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and even from afar I could see a huge --", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "huge pile of folded objects on top of her desk.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was like, wow, she really knows what she&#39;s doing.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I stood up, and I started to walk towards her.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when I got there, I was very surprised.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because nothing caught my eyes.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There were a lot of objects on top of her desk,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but none of them seemed very impressive,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I was like, this is it?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I tapped her on her shoulder and said,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What are you making?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And she said, &quot;I don&#39;t know&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m like, &quot;Well, what are all these objects,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what are they?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And she said, &quot;I don&#39;t know, I&#39;m just trying stuff out&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I couldn&#39;t believe her!", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, she did not know, how could her hands be moving?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If she did not know, how could she decide where to fold", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and in what direction?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If she did not know, how could she predict what effect her", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fold could have on all the subsequent folds?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ Laughter ]", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So at that point it dawned on me, this was youth.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s what was meant by having a beginner&#39;s mindset.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was humility.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Never mind my lack of drawing skills,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "humility is what I really lacked.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see all this time I thought making was something you do", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to produce a product.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A means to an end.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But no, making was going through a process", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with enough humility to admit that you do not know,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "yet having enough confidence", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to not let anyone convince you that you&#39;re crazy.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It didn&#39;t matter whether she thought she knew", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or not, she was making.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just because she didn&#39;t,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "she didn&#39;t know where she was headed,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it did not mean she was lost.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just because she couldn&#39;t articulate her goals,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it did not mean she lacked purpose.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when I realized this, I couldn&#39;t help but wonder,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has much of my professional life has made me into a,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an arrogant, dogmatic adult?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Stupefied by his own experience?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then a year and a half passed by,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I was now sitting in an acting class.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was watching my friends rehearse for a play called,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;A Streetcar Named Desire&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the scene was where the, the male character, Stanley,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "aggressively interrogates the female character, Blanche.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I, the night before,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had actually watched the movie version of the scene", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where Marlon Brando and Vivien Leigh plays these roles,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I kind of knew what to expect.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to be honest, my friends were sucking really bad.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And bad acting is kind of hard to watch.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, eventually the director stops them, and she says,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and she looks at my friend playing Blanche and goes,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What&#39;s going on in your mind", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as you&#39;re playing the role of Blanche?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my friend goes, &quot;Well,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m trying to put myself in her shoes.&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the director goes, &quot;Okay,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how do you think Blanche is feeling?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My friend goes, &quot;Defensive?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the director goes, &quot;What else?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my friend goes, &quot;Vulnerable?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then the director pauses for a second and says,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Have you ever been in front of another man", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that made you feel so vulnerable that you felt the need", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to defend yourself?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my friend pauses for a second, and she says, &quot;Yes&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the entire room goes silent.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the director starts asking more questions.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What was the day like?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Was it hot or cold?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;How tall was he?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What was the color of his skin?&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;You don&#39;t have to answer out loud,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just remember what it was like.&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And before I know it, my friend begins to weep.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the director says,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Take that with you and say the lines&quot;.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as difficult as this must have been", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for my friend, she does it.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what came out was a beautiful performance.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see all this time I thought acting was telling somebody", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "else&#39;s story.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But no, acting was having enough courage to tell your story.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Of course the name of the character, the situation,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the costume, none of those were yours,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the experience that lined the foundation", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of your performance, that was all yours.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when such sincere honesty was perceived, I,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as an audience member, could not help", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but feel a profound sense of resonance, of connection.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because despite all the superficial differences I perceived", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of her, I could recognize an unmistakable quality", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of shared humanity.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, the conclusion I arrived at in my research was", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that at the heart of all creative processes is empathy.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Think of the story of the paper folding exercise.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When we try to empathize with another,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "instead of treating them as a problem", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to be solved, we listen to them.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When we try to empathize with another,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "instead of telling them what to do, we let them surprise us.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She was doing the same with her materials.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And just as that interaction,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or the memory of that interaction,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "helps us feel a sense of connection to others,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the same was happening between her and her materials.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She was developing empathy in relation to her materials.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The same was true of my friend in the acting class.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She was developing empathy in relation", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to an imaginary character.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I want you to think about that.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But what I found most remarkable about going", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "through such a creative process is that as you&#39;re trying", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to empathize with these others,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it actually helps you better understand yourself.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Have you ever had an experience", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where you&#39;re trying really hard to write clearly", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for other people, and it actually helps you better", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "understand what you&#39;re thinking?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Have you ever had an experience where you try", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to teach somebody something,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it actually helps you better understand what you&#39;re", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "trying to teach?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, trying to empathize with another", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the creative context is intrinsically reciprocal.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not reciprocal in the sense of exchanging gifts or favors,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but in the sense that the act of giving is in", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and of itself an act of receiving.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is neither selfish nor altruistic.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s simply a loop that cannot be untangled", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without losing its meaning.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is at the heart of any, this is a cardiac cycle", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of any creative relationships.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is what makes the process of making just as,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if not more, meaningful than the product.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what I&#39;d like to do in closing is to challenge you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to take a moment today,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and think about what going further means", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to you in your journey.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you&#39;re unsure where you&#39;re going,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I want you to remember the first story,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of having the humility to admit", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you don&#39;t know while having enough confidence", 
